<span id="freeTextContainer270128778927548643">This book deserves 4 stars, the extra star is because to understand the book, I had to first read The book of disquiet and then spend days reading up on the history of Portugal to get the context of the book. And I&apos;ve emerged so much richer for having read it.</span>
  <span id="freeText270128778927548643" style="display:none">This book deserves 4 stars, the extra star is because to understand the book, I had to first read The book of disquiet and then spend days reading up on the history of Portugal to get the context of the book. And I've emerged so much richer for having read it.</span>
